per human DALY, times the suffering per factory-farmed life-year, times the animal&#x27;s welfare range. Under a heavy animal welfare range the penalty can exceed the human benefit, so saving human lives looks net-harmful. Only bites once animals count, so it requires animals_somewhat; and it is a near-term human-vs-animal get-off point, not combined with astronomical-stakes longtermism (no_discounting_future_humans), where x-risk dominates and the meat bookkeeping is moot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 6 suffering_focused → 7 meat_eater_problem" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vm1z4jYQ%2Fis7TDuFFIhNICR0%2BEAS8jLH9TI52ptOyHDCXmP1ZMkjyXFoLv%2B9KxsCBPjAYLyrZ3effXbFayXEiGXCXqoQK73K8TH0%2B30Ya8YlWAWBZv8t6CGXMMlant%2BGXGkRPnPMIfenrenptAtVY1UK3Zo7OpEEMTAmS1LLlYQgJqQeeJAyrYKYM%2BGA%2FPMW%2BBAxPWU5W0zjLGHSrAwtYJInTJipUQnmMbMryymYLIpQczmfRirIDIYrUxcSZHZKH9TTVKuZwKTIZciCGNg6IW6Awf3CxvQccYFAha7N5hisC8jC0NRBI7HDJRpQugDT2KA6WIIUhRt6b2MsS%2FzNQJTJoMD4AwKVpMpQmmsHOitDJER6xU2BZiyTIRNKIiREv2jC93d2h8%2FfXaruOL6kGFg6%2BMxEhqCiAmHdiGYBdoHGwixbQObCuIMGNwvrwZiwbh3TCCNk8wzLgzfDP4cPg%2FHwCmYLmKNETRw208Wq4Rhyu8XQERnrIJUt83AkElKBdcU1pQpITaIvYhgd%2B0rPiZ5UU1P1AmYUIuIBp%2Bc6XAyvvzwMqXzNRIGQI5%2FHlpgjMoRyEoz597JpQs2l0iQMOPd%2Bhcs7qCpNpTZU1EjYXHKbhQgXX8bDyxrlY1SWfuI2iFFeMbG4R%2F2XCaEPrxMJkKJKBd6iSDF8t3hNr%2BMCes2O88lRiBlSJjfUPQdRunh%2B6eP5zilQmSQtRCywGRMXTP74u2iScz05EOloD%2FQRVH1oHIKrTeTbRM7DrUJcLl57mYzXmkiWRDsOJ8uKvBaly3iy47CqpkU121hs2f1my1nbXWIzT7dNLc9ztm6bkpjInItwls3Nts9p6XPWKnyYEBHultB6p5xmI1fqo0dhdwjeUmPDx%2FxqMPoH2DNqNxUpqf2Xp96m1MItGVqeLCd1LbNAkZFEiNJ%2BmCY6zj6sL0gza5yauXXCCpSb4j48uv6%2BAvGOPZhURiogaTrZwY9Sd5NKHfLwvZyeW1GyuleYNVIAKQZ%2Bh2qj0%2Bx2z07b2PA6NXirb0e54c9YTplY7MfflMkmbKEX3%2FPPu%2Bf7Yb%2BRKsFtcipac7uA6uDzdW1%2FkC2tuSjrGL7ndc72hBjcfYZjuFxiD6XVmNJOxEybmKcHwmwqdqeYM%2F%2F0xD%2FbjbSz6PaDb8m9BPc7fvekvQP4NabdlQIRRFcWwr1W%2F1IDDrR3c1IK1B24bzQtdO0YwjBQjctMU9rfJMgQzQHKd2dsP%2FpgNLoeXh3g88MMHkC4A8MidAp4KGcSHug2YTqID%2BS2M7pr4C